StmtSimple.StatementText: MERGE INTO WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon.history.MeasureResultProvider mrp USING ( Select job_key as LineageId ,mr.MeasureResultsId as MeasureResultId ,providerM.Id as ProviderMasterId FROM WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon.cqms.processed_measure_status_provider pmsp INNER JOIN #measureResultsWithCqmsIds mr ON pmsp.measure_id = mr.cqmsMeasureId AND pmsp.patient_source_key = mr.cqmsPatientId AND pmsp.visit_source_key = mr.cqmsVisitId INNER JOIN WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon.history.ProviderMaster providerM ON pmsp.provider_source_key = providerM.AdvisoryMDMKey WHERE pmsp.provider_source_key != '-1' AND pmsp.job_key = '000E2C72-E027-4272-BC3A-5C9AA1AA81BD' ) cqmsResults ON mrp.LineageId = cqmsResults.LineageId AND mrp.MeasureResultId = cqmsResults.MeasureResultId AND mrp.ProviderMasterId = cqmsResults.ProviderMasterId WHEN NOT MATCHED BY TARGET THEN INSERT ( RecordCreated ,RecordModified,RecordStatus ,LineageId, MeasureResultId, ProviderMasterId ) VALUES (CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 'A' ,cqmsResults.LineageId , cqmsResults.MeasureResultId, cqmsResults.ProviderMasterId );

ScalarOperator.ScalarString: [WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon].[history].[MeasureResultProvider].[ProviderMasterId] as [mrp].[ProviderMasterId] = [WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon].[history].[ProviderMaster].[Id] as [providerM].[Id],[WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon].[history].[MeasureResultProvider].[RecordStatus] as [mrp].[RecordStatus] = [Expr1009],[WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon].[history].[MeasureResultProvider].[LineageId] as [mrp].[LineageId] = [WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon].[cqms].[processed_measure_status_provider].[job_key] as [pmsp].[job_key],[WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon].[history].[MeasureResultProvider].[RecordModified] as [mrp].[RecordModified] = [Expr1010],[WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon].[history].[MeasureResultProvider].[RecordCreated] as [mrp].[RecordCreated] = [Expr1011],[WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon].[history].[MeasureResultProvider].[MeasureResultId] as [mrp].[MeasureResultId] = [tempdb].[dbo].[#measureResultsWithCqmsIds].[MeasureResultsId] as [mr].[MeasureResultsId],[WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon].[history].[MeasureResultProvider].[Id] as [mrp].[Id] = RaiseIfNullUpdate([Expr1008]),[WesternConnecticut_Danbury_Canon].[history].[MeasureResultProvider].[ProviderId] as [mrp].[ProviderId] = [Expr1012]
ForceOrder(CASE WHEN [TrgPrb1005] IS NOT NULL THEN NULL ELSE (4) END)
